Vultr,provides,users,with,access,to,cloud,based,servers,on,which,they,can,deploy,their,virtual,machines,Once,an,order,is,placed,instances,can,be,spun,within,seconds,Users,can,choose,from,a,wide,range,of,operating,system,templates,or,upload,their,own,Vultr,s,control,panel,offers,one,click,access,to,important,functions,such,as,restarting,rebooting,and,reinstalling,Users,are,billed,by,the,hour,with,no,long,term,contracts,The,Vultr,API,enables,users,to,manage,their,infrastructure,from,third,party,systems